{"title":"fix(remediation): correct Deployment selector matchLabels for vigil-app","body":"Root cause: Deployment selector mismatch - spec.selector.matchLabels uses 'vigil-app-typo' but template labels use 'vigil-app', causing immutable field validation failure.

Evidence: Deployment.apps "vigil-app" is invalid: [spec.template.metadata.labels: Invalid value: {"app":"vigil-app"}: `selector` does not match template `labels`, spec.selector: Invalid value: {"matchLabels":{"app":"vigil-app-typo"}}: field is immutable]

This fix corrects the selector to match the template labels."}
